000600*    VALIDATION FOR:-                                          *  ST1054.2
000700*                                                              *  ST1054.2
000800*    "ON-SITE VALIDATION, NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF STD & TECH.     ".ST1054.2
000900*                                                              *  ST1054.2
