053500     MOVE CCVS-C-2 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE 2 TIMES.   ST1084.2
053600     MOVE HYPHEN-LINE TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE.        ST1084.2
