059800     MOVE   SPACES TO INF-ANSI-REFERENCE.                         ST1084.2
059900     GO TO  FAIL-ROUTINE-EX.                                      ST1084.2
060000 FAIL-ROUTINE-WRITE.                                              ST1084.2
