061500 CCVS1-EXIT.                                                      ST1084.2
061600     EXIT.                                                        ST1084.2
061700 OUTPROC-EXIT SECTION.                                            ST1084.2
061800 EXIT-ONLY.                                                       ST1084.2
061900     PERFORM  CLOSE-FILES.                                        ST1084.2
