049400     PERFORM  PRINT-DETAIL.                                       ST1114.2
049500 CCVS-EXIT SECTION.                                               ST1114.2
049600 CCVS-999999.                                                     ST1114.2
049700     GO TO CLOSE-FILES.                                           ST1114.2
