002100*    ST118 IS A COMPLETELY SELF-CONTAINED PROGRAM.  THE INPUT     ST1184.2
002200*    PROCEDURE BUILDS THE EIGHT-RECORD FILE SHOWN BELOW. THE      ST1184.2
