002400*    REPORT.                                                      ST1184.2
002500*    SORT    SORT    SORT    SORT    SORT   SORT     SORT    SORT ST1184.2
002600*    KEY-1   KEY-2   KEY-3   KEY-4   KEY-5  KEY-6    KEY-7   KEY-8ST1184.2
002700*    S9(6)   A(5)    SV9(16) X(10)   A(20)  X(10)    999     S99  ST1184.2
