001300*                                                              *  ST1324.2
001400*      X-CARDS USED BY THIS PROGRAM ARE :-                     *  ST1324.2
001500*                                                              *  ST1324.2
001600*        X-55  - SYSTEM PRINTER NAME.                          *  ST1324.2
001700*        X-82  - SOURCE COMPUTER NAME.                         *  ST1324.2
