000400****************************************************************  ST1354.2
000500*                                                              *  ST1354.2
000600*    VALIDATION FOR:-                                          *  ST1354.2
000700*                                                              *  ST1354.2
000800*    "ON-SITE VALIDATION, NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF STD & TECH.     ".ST1354.2
000900*                                                              *  ST1354.2
