049300     MOVE    ZERO TO REC-SKL-SUB.                                 ST1404.2
049400     PERFORM CCVS-INIT-FILE 9 TIMES.                              ST1404.2
049500 CCVS-INIT-FILE.                                                  ST1404.2
049600     ADD     1 TO REC-SKL-SUB.                                    ST1404.2
