051100 FAIL.  MOVE "FAIL*" TO P-OR-F.  ADD 1 TO ERROR-COUNTER.          ST1444.2
051200 DE-LETE.  MOVE "*****" TO P-OR-F.  ADD 1 TO DELETE-COUNTER.      ST1444.2
051300     MOVE "****TEST DELETED****" TO RE-MARK.                      ST1444.2
