056700     MOVE CCVS-E-3 TO DUMMY-RECORD. PERFORM WRITE-LINE.           ST1444.2
056800 WRITE-LINE.                                                      ST1444.2
056900     ADD 1 TO RECORD-COUNT.                                       ST1444.2
057000     IF RECORD-COUNT GREATER 42                                   ST1444.2
