057400         MOVE CCVS-H-1  TO DUMMY-RECORD PERFORM WRT-LN 2 TIMES    ST1444.2
057500         MOVE CCVS-H-2A TO DUMMY-RECORD PERFORM WRT-LN 2 TIMES    ST1444.2
